<p>
<strong>About The Resumator</strong></p>
<p>
The Resumator is a quirky, Pittsburgh-based software company that is reinventing the way employers hire. Featured on TechCrunch, Mashable and CNET, we empower growing businesses with recruiting tools they&#39;ve never had, but have always needed. Our 1000+ customers include some of the fastest growing businesses and hottest startups in the world like Pinterest, Instagram, Klout, and HootSuite.</p>
<p>
Included in Entrepreneur magazine&rsquo;s list of &ldquo;100 Brilliant Companies,&rdquo; The Resumator has been widely heralded as an innovative, essential product for businesses that need to hire. The Resumator has been called a &ldquo;life-changing&rdquo; service and &ldquo;one of the best SaaS tools I&rsquo;ve ever used.&rdquo; Our software interface is beautiful. Our customer demos are a love-fest. We&rsquo;re building a great company where people want to come to work, and we&rsquo;re looking for creative, battle-tested people to join our team!</p>
<p>
Most importantly, we are an entrepreneurial-focused company. We want all of our folks to learn what it takes to start their own business someday, which means much of our company information is transparent. This is an excellent opportunity to gain skills to someday manage your own products.</p>
<p>
